EntityViewProcessorRegistry
public final class EntityViewProcessorRegistry.EntityViewProcessorRegistration extends Object implements org.springframework.core.Ordered
Represents a processor entry in the factory. A processor is identifiable by name and can (optionally) have an order. If no explicit order is given, they will be kept in order they are registered in.
